                        <h5 class="card-title">Tips for On-time Payments</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Sign-up for text/email notifications.</li>
                            <li>Most service providers have an auto-pay option if you're forget-ful.</li>
                            <li>Set calendar reminders.</li>
                            <li>If you can, pay bills as soon as they are available.</li>
                            <li>If not, start with the smaller payments first.</li>
                        </ul>
            
                    </div>
                </div>
