                        <h5 class="card-title">Tips for Loans</h5>
                        <h6>Loans can be scary, take these!</h6>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Most loans require a certain minimum credit score to be considered. Do some research first!</li>
                            <li>Part of the process for applying for loans is a hard credit check, which always hurts your credit. And this can be detrimental
                                if you aren't sure you will get the loan.
                            </li>
                            <li>Loan monthly payments should never take a majority of your available income. Make sure you have enough to go into your savings!</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center col-sm-3 mb-3 col-lg-3 mb-sm-0 my-4 option-card">
