                    <div class="card-body">

                        <h5 class="card-title">Tips for Credit Cards</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Don't open too many credit cards. Each one you open initiates a hard credit check which hurts!</li>
                            <li>Don't make the minimum payment each month, this is a trap! Although it will save you from getting demerits, it doesn't get you any closer to 
                                your goal of paying off the credit loan.
                            </li>
                            <li>Try to keep 10% of your total available credit in use. This is because having some debt helps your credit more than having no debt, while also 
                                not coming with a ridiculous interest amount.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
